headline: Is Morgan Stanley Still a Good Pick After Surging 25% in 2025?
summary: If you have been watching Morgan Stanley recently, you are not alone. With many investors trying to figure out whether now is the right time to buy, hold, or cash out, the conversation has gotten interesting. Over the past five years, Morgan Stanley’s stock has soared an incredible 266.8%, and in just the past twelve months, jumped another 63.9%. Even more impressive, just this year, the shares have surged 25.3% already, catching the eye of both growth-minded investors and those seeking...
